title: Surgeon Simulator Anniversary Edition Inside Donald Trump-TiNYiS
description:
Proudly Presents

Surgeon Simulator Anniversary Edition: Inside Donald Trump (c) Bossa Studios
Release On: 4 June 2016 Disk Amount/Format: 1 DVD
Type of Game: Action Media Protection: Steam

`Inside Donald Trump' allows you to step into the hands of a master
surgeon, dedicated to saving Mr Trump's life by replacing his ailing
heart - but will you replace it with a heart of gold, or a heart of
stone? THE CHOICE IS YOURS! There are lots of new professional-grade
medical tools to help you with your surgery; you can ease Donald's
medicated sleep using Trump Vodka, gently caress him with a meaty
Trump Steak or loosen his organs with the Trump Tower, plus a few
other Trump-related surprises (some of them involving hands)

NOTE:

This is made standalone, updated to latest build and feature all DLC
released to date

You access the Inside Donald Trump DLC by checking the desk/using the
remote

Burn/mount, install, copy crack, play!
